MAX17261 Fuel Gauge Driver
A modular driver for the MAX17261 ModelGauge m5 EZ fuel gauge IC using Arduino and I²C communication.
Overview
This project implements a configurable driver supporting battery measurements, alert registers, status registers, configuration registers, calibration registers, and interactive reserved register lookup.
Features
•	Cell Voltage (VCELL)
•	Average Voltage (AVGVCELL)
•	Current and Average Current
•	Temperature Measurements
•	SOC and Battery Age
•	Capacity Registers
•	Time-To-Empty and Time-To-Full
•	Alert Threshold Registers
•	STATUS, STATUS2 and FSTAT Registers
•	Configuration Registers
•	Calibration Registers
•	Interactive Reserved Register Lookup
Reserved Register Lookup
User enters a hexadecimal address through Serial Monitor.

Example:
30  → REG 0x30 : 0x0C01
E4  → REG 0xE4 : 0x00B3
